name: Dr. Carlos' Personality Exam
description:
Take the test that everyone is raving about: The Dr. Carlos Personality Exam.

In it, you will be forced to face the harsh reality of your meager existence, through a series of mind bending questions.

Features include:

- IQ assessment.
- Spirit Animal.
- Personality Type.
- Over 59 questions.
- Test can be repeated multiple times for maximum effectiveness.

Do you have the GUTS to take on Dr. Carlos?
